What you need to know:

Rabbit farming has great potential as an agribusiness.Rabbits can be kept in any part of the country for as long as they are housed properly, fed well and protected from predators. The cost of production majorly relies on the system employed for production. They feed on pellets, which can be supplemented with greens and other edible herbs, which provide them vitamins. Offer them enough clean water to ease digestion. 